				When enabled, allows you to craft the weapon with 20 of any Wood and 2 Copper/Tin Bars at any Anvil.
				(Works well with the damage scaling option enabled!)
				'''
		}

		ScalingDamage: {
			Label: Damage Scaling Mode
			Tooltip:
				'''
				When enabled, forces the weapon to start at 12 damage, but scales damage
